;What is Firefox OS?
Ko woni Firefox OS?


;Backed by some of the biggest names in the industry, Firefox OS is a new open operating system for smartphones developed by Mozilla.
E gollondiral e yoga e inɗe ɓurɗe mawnude e jeere cinnde, Firefox OS ko yuɓɓo yuuɓnungo heso udditiingo ndognoowu cinnde ngo Mozilla topii.


;Built entirely using HTML5 and other open Web standards, Firefox OS is free from the rules and restrictions of existing proprietary platforms.
Topiraa e kuuɓal ko HTML5 e gaadaneeje Geese udditiiɗe goɗɗe, Firefox OS ena rimɗi e kuule e tiwaaɗe dinndeeje keeroraaɗi jeyal.


;How is Firefox OS different from other operating systems?
Hol no Firefox OS seertiri e yuɓɓooji kuuɓnuɗi goɗɗi?


;Firefox OS is the only operating system with Adaptive App Search.
Firefox OS woni wooto e yuɓɓooji kuuɓnuɗi jogiingo Njiylaw Jaaɓɗe Jamminoowo.


;While every other phone today is static, giving you the exact same apps each time you turn it on, Firefox OS is always changing to offer exactly the apps you need at any moment in your life.
Cinnde keewɗe hannde nde wonnoo ngonaa ɓosooje, ɗo ndokkat-maa ko jaaɓɗe goote tan sahaa kala nde ɗe kuɓɓa, Firefox OS kañum koko waylotoo sahaa kala ngam hokkude-ma jaaɓɗe ɗe coklu-ɗaa tuma kala e nguurndam maa.


;It adapts so you can live every moment to its fullest.
O jamminoto ngam mbaawaa wuurde sahngaaji kala no haanirta.


;Firefox OS is brought to you by Mozilla, a global nonprofit organization that emphasizes principle over profit.
Firefox OS addan-maa ɗum ko Mozilla, fedde huuɓnunde nde ɗaɓɓaani ngalu nde aadi ɓurani ɗum tiiɗde e dañal.


;We believe that the Web is a shared public resource to be cared for, not a commodity to be sold.
Amin ngoongɗiɗi wonde Geese ɗee koko ndenndaa tee ena poti toppiteede, wonaa jawdi njeeyeteendi.


;We work with a worldwide community to create open source products like Mozilla Firefox and to innovate for the benefit of the individual and the betterment of the Web.
Amin ngollotoo e renndo aduyaŋkoore nfam tafde topirɗe ari-topoo wano Mozilla Firefox kadi e addude kesamaagu mbele mo woni kala ena naftoroo haa wona ɓural Geese ɗee.


;The result is great products built by passionate people and better choices for everyone.
Njualtudi golle amen ko topirɗe tafaaɗe e juuɗe yimɓe goongɗimɓe adduɓe cuɓe ɓurɗe yuɓɓande mo woni kala.


